@startuml
title Partner search cold deck and swipe - sequence diagram

actor User
participant "Search page" as FE
participant "gRPC Gateway" as Gateway
participant "PartnerSearchService" as Search
participant "Community UserService" as Community
database "MongoDB" as Mongo

User -> FE : opens Search page
FE -> Gateway : GET /v1/search/cold/deck?user_id=...
Gateway -> Search : GetColdDeck(user_id, filters)
Search -> Mongo : query active ColdForms
Search -> Search : exclude owner_id=user_id
Search -> Search : exclude liked/disliked/blocked by user
Search -> Search : apply role, server, rank filters
Search -> Community : GetUser(owner_id) for previews
Community --> Search : OwnerPreview data
Search --> Gateway : ColdDeckResponse(forms)
Gateway --> FE : card deck

User -> FE : swipes Like / Dislike / Block
FE -> Gateway : POST /v1/search/cold/{form_id}/swipe
Gateway -> Search : SwipeColdForm(form_id, user_id, action)
Search -> Mongo : add user_id to liked_by/disliked_by/blocked_by
Search --> Gateway : SwipeFormResponse
Gateway --> FE : success
FE -> FE : invalidate cold deck query
FE -> Gateway : GET next cold deck

@enduml
